   ['But when he saw many of the Pharisees and Sadducees coming to his immersion*, he said to them, Offspring of vipers, who warned you* to flee from the future wrath?'],
   ['Therefore you* produce fruit worthy of repentance.'],
   ['Do not think to say among yourselves, We have Abraham for our father; for* I say to you* that God is able to lift up children out of these stones for Abraham.'],
   ['And even already, the ax is lying to the root of the trees, because every tree which is not producing good fruit is cut down and cast into the fire.'],
