   ['Then Jesus says to him, <font color=#FF0000>Go behind me, adversary! For</font><font color=#FF0000>*</font><font color=#FF0000> it has been written, &lsquo;You will worship the Lord your God and you will give-divine service to him only.&rsquo; </font><font color=#808080>{Deut. 6:13}</font>'],
