   ['the people who sat in darkness saw a great light and to those who sat in the region and shadow of death, light has risen for them.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Is. 9:1f}</font> <font color=#808080>{Mk 1:14b-15 &amp; Mt 4:17 &amp; Lk 4:14b-15}</font>'],
   ['From then onward, Jesus began to preach and to say, <font color=#FF0000>Repent; for</font><font color=#FF0000>*</font><font color=#FF0000> the kingdom of heaven has drawn near.</font> <font color=#808080>{Mk 1:16-20 &amp; Mt 4:18-22 &amp; Lk 5:1-11 Sea of Galilee near Capernaum</font><font color=#808080>.}</font>'],
   ['And walking by the sea of Galilee, he saw two brethren, Simon who is called Peter and Andrew, his brother, casting a net into the sea; for* they were fishermen.'],
   ['And he says to them, <font color=#FF0000>Come-here after me and I will make</font><font color=#FF0000>*</font><font color=#FF0000> you</font><font color=#FF0000>*</font><font color=#FF0000> fishermen of men.</font>'],
