   ['And they immediately left the ship and their father and followed him.<font color=#808080> {Mk 1:35-39 &amp; Mt 4:23-25 &amp; Lk 4:42-44 Preaching through Galilee</font><font color=#808080>}</font>'],
   ['And Jesus went around all Galilee, teaching in their synagogues and preaching the good-news of the kingdom and healing all kinds of disease and all kinds of illness among the people.'],
