   ['And they beat his head with a reed and spit on him and placing their knees down, worshiped him.<font color=#808080> {Mk 15:20-23 &amp; Mt 27:31-34 &amp; Lk 23:26-33 &amp; Jn 19:17 Road to the Cross, Friday morning</font><font color=#808080>}</font><font color=#808080></font>'],
   ['And when they had mocked him, they stripped the purple off him and clothed him with his own garments. And they lead him out that* they should crucify him.'],
