   ['And they crucify two robbers with him; one at his right and one at his left.'],
   ['And the Scripture was fulfilled, which says &lsquo;And he was counted with the lawless.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Is. 53:12}</font>'],
   ['And those who traveled by blasphemed him, wagging their heads and saying, Ha! You who will tear-down the temple and build it in three days,'],
