   ['And when it became the sixth hour, there was darkness over the whole earth until the ninth hour<font color=#808080>.</font> {Mk 15:34-41 &amp; Mt 27:46-56 &amp; Lk 23:45-49 &amp; Jn 19:28-30 around 5:00 PM}'],
   ['And in the ninth hour Jesus cried with a loud voice, saying,<font color=#FF0000> Eloi, Eloi, lama sabachthani?</font> which is, after being translated, &lsquo;My God, my God, why have you forsaken me?&rsquo;<font color=#808080> </font><font color=#808080>{Ps. 22:1}</font>'],
