   ['<font color=#FF0000>they will lift up serpents and even if they drink anything deadly, it may never</font><font color=#FF0000>*</font><font color=#FF0000> harm them; they will lay hands upon </font><i><font color=#FF0000>the</font></i><font color=#FF0000> sick and they will be well.</font><font color=#808080> {Lk 24:44-49 &amp; Acts 1:3-8 &amp; 1Cor: 15:7 Jerusalem</font><font color=#808080>}</font><font color=#808080></font> {Mk 16:19-20 &amp; Lk 24:50-53 &amp; Acts 1:9-12 Olivet, between Jerusalem and Bethany<font color=#808080>}</font>'],
