   ['And the Spirit said to Philip, <font color=#FF0000>Go near and join yourself to this chariot.</font><font color=#808080> {Acts 2:14-42; 8:5-13; 8:30-39; 9:17-18, 22:6-14, 26:12-18; 10:34-38; 16:25-34; 16:13; 18:8-9; 19:1-7. Examples of those who were saved in the New Testament.}</font>'],
