  [ // 45:9
   ['I say the truth in Christ, I am not lying, my conscience is testifying with me in the Holy Spirit,'],
   ['that I have great sorrow and constant anguish in my heart.'],
   ['For* I would pray that I myself were accursed from Christ on behalf of my brethren, my relatives according to the flesh,'],
   ['who are Israelites, whose is the sonship and the glory and the covenants* and the institution of the law and the divine service and the promises;'],
   ['whose are the fathers and from whom is Christ according to the flesh, who is over all: God is gracious* forever. Amen.'],
   ['But it is not such-as that the word of God has fallen short. For* they are not all Israel, (those who are from Israel);'],
   ['nor, are they all children, because they are Abraham&rsquo;s seed, but, &lsquo;In Isaac your seed will be called.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Gen. 21:12}</font>'],
   ['That is, it is not the children of the flesh who are children of God, but the children of the promise are counted *for a seed.'],
   ['For* this is the word of promise, &lsquo;I will come according to this season and Sarah will have a son.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Gen. 18:10}</font>'],
