   ['But I say, &lsquo;Did they not hear?&rsquo; But-rather, &lsquo;Their sounds went out into all the earth and their words to the ends of the inhabited-earth.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Ps. 19:4}</font>'],
   ['But I say, Did Israel not know? First Moses says, &lsquo;I will provoke you* to jealousy with what is no nation. I will rouse you* to anger with a nation which has no understanding.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Deut. 32:21}</font>'],
   ['And Isaiah is very daring and says, &lsquo;I was found by those who are not seeking me. I became manifest to those who are not asking for me.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Is. 65:1}</font>'],
