   ['And this is my covenant* to them, when I may take away their sins.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Is. 59:20-21, 27:9}</font>'],
   ['<i>They are</i> enemies because of you* according to the good-news, but according to the choice, they are beloved because of the fathers.'],
