   ['If possible, what is from you should be at peace with all men.'],
   ['Beloved, do not be avenging yourselves, but give a chance for the wrath of God; for* it has been written, &lsquo;Vengeance is for me. I will repay, says the Lord.&rsquo; <font color=#808080>{Deut. 32:25}</font>'],
