   ['<i>This was</i> according to the everlasting purpose which he made* in Christ Jesus our Lord;'],
   ['in whom we have boldness and access in confidence through his faith.'],
   ['Hence I ask you* not to be depressed at my afflictions on your* behalf, which are your* glory.'],
