  [ // 49:5
   ['Therefore become imitators of God, as beloved children,'],
   ['and walk in love*, just-as Christ also loved* us and gave himself up on our behalf as an offering and a sacrifice to God *for an aroma of a sweet-fragrance.'],
   ['But do not let fornication and all uncleanness or greed be even named among you*, as is suitable to holy-ones;'],
