  [ // 51:4
   ['Lords, provide what is just and equal to your* bondservants; knowing that you* also have a Lord in the heavens.'],
   ['Persevere in prayer, watching in it, with thanksgiving;'],
   ['praying at the same time concerning us also, that* God may open a door of the word to us, to speak the mystery of Christ, because of which I have also been bound;'],
