   ['to which I was appointed* a preacher and an apostle and a teacher of the Gentiles.'],
   ['Because of which cause, I also am suffering these things too, but I am not ashamed; for* I know him whom I have believed and I have been persuaded that he is able to guard the deposit consigned to me *for that day.'],
   ['Hold to the pattern of sound* words which you have heard from me, in faith and love* which is in Christ Jesus.'],
   ['Guard the good deposit consigned to you through the Holy Spirit who is dwelling in us.'],
   ['You know this, that all who are in Asia turned away from me; of whom are Phygelus and Hermogenes.'],
