  [ // 55:2
   ['Therefore you, my child, be empowered with the grace that is in Christ Jesus.'],
   ['And the things which you have heard from me among many witnesses, intrust these to faithful men, who will also be competent to teach others.'],
   ['Therefore you suffer evil treatment as a good soldier of Jesus the Christ.'],
   ['No active soldier entangles himself in the <font color=#808080>{F}</font> tradeoffs of this life, that* he may please the one who enlisted him as a soldier.'],
   ['And if anyone also contends in the games, he is not crowned, if he has not contended lawfully.'],
   ['The farmer must labor first to receive of the fruits.'],
   ['Perceive the things I am saying; for* the Lord may give you understanding in all things.'],
   ['Remember Jesus the Christ, who arose from the dead, was born out of the seed of David, according to my good-news;'],
   ['in which I am suffering evil treatment, even as far as bonds, like a criminal, but the word of God is not bound.'],
