   ['But even all who wish to live devoutly in Christ Jesus will be persecuted.'],
   ['But wicked men and impostors will progress from bad to worse, misleading and being misled.'],
   ['But you abide in the things which you have learned and were entrusted with, having known from whom you have learned them.'],
