   ['Greet Prisca and Aquila and the house of Onesiphorus.'],
   ['Erastus remained in Corinth, but I left Trophimus sick in Miletus.'],
   ['Be diligent to come before winter. Eubulus greets you and Pudens and Linus and Claudia and all the brethren.'],
   ['The Lord Jesus the Christ, be with your spirit. Grace be with you*. Amen.'],
