   ['For* it was suitable for him, because whom are all things and through whom are all things, in bringing many sons to glory, to perfect the author of their salvation through sufferings.'],
   ['For* both he who is sanctifying and those who are sanctified are all from one. Because of which cause, he is not ashamed to call them brethren,'],
