  [ // 58:3
   ['Hence, holy brethren, partakers of a heavenly calling, consider Jesus the Christ, the Apostle and High-Priest of our confession;'],
   ['who was faithful to him who made* him such, as Moses also was in all his house.'],
   ['For* he has been deemed worthy of more glory than Moses, inasmuch as the one who constructed the house has more honor than the house.'],
