  [ // 62:4
   ['Beloved, do not believe every spirit, but test the spirits, to see if they are from God, because many false prophets have gone out into the world.'],
   ['You* know by this the Spirit of God. Every spirit which confesses that Jesus the Christ has come in the flesh is from God;'],
   ['and every spirit that does not confess Jesus the Christ as having come in the flesh, is not from God and this is the spirit of the antichrist, which you* have heard of, that it is coming, and now it is already in the world.'],
   ['You* are from God, my little children and have overcome them, because greater is he who is in you* than he who is in the world.'],
   ['They are from the world. Therefore they speak as from the world and the world hears them.'],
   ['We are from God. He who knows God, hears us; he who is not from God does not hear us. We know from this, <font color=#808080>{F}</font> the spirit of the truth and the spirit of the deceit.'],
   ['Beloved, we should love* one another, because love* is from God, and everyone who loves* has been born from God and knows God.'],
